title: BREAKING: US court DENIES Trump’s request to immediately reinstate ‘Muslim’ travel ban
text:
BREAKING: US court DENIES Trump’s request to immediately reinstate ‘Muslim’ travel ban BREAKING: US court DENIES Trump’s request to immediately reinstate ‘Muslim’ travel ban THE US appeals court has denied US President Donald Trump's request to immediately reinstate his travel ban. PUBLISHED: 09:04, Sun, Feb 5, 2017 | UPDATED: 09:14, Sun, Feb 5, 2017 Getty US President Donald Trump at work in the White House 
More follows.
